  title: Negotiation
  description: "\u201C<i>Where is my wife?</i>\u201D Frank is now standing fully
    in the open doorway. You can see that he is carrying a firearm in his right hand.
    And that he is holding the secretary hostage. \r\n\r\nTrying to remain calm you
    say, \u201C<i>It is taking some time to reach her.</i>\u201D\r\n\r\nMr. Parks
    walks back inside upset. You take a few steps closer to the doorway.\r\n\r\n\u201C<i>Frank?</i>\u201D
    You raise your voice again concerned.\r\n\r\n<margin=2em>\r\n1 ) For the safety
    of the secretary you shout, \"Frank! Please do not harm Ms. Weber!\"\n\n2 ) You
    draw your weapon.\n\n3 ) \u201C<i>I understand your frustration.</i>\u201D\r\n</margin>
    \r\n"
